{
  "stem": "894.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But I do remember, though, one incident which is enough to give you nightmares-- give me nightmares for the rest of my life-- is that I got up, one day-- one night, in the middle of the night.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was very dark.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I got out of the bunk.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I went outside, to the bathroom, which was a very makeshift kind of a thing.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I was standing all alone there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And it was very quiet.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I saw this huge, huge chimney.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And the flames were just going out of it like-- and I was standing there mesmerized.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I mean, I remember the very thoughts that I thought at the time.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I said, my god, these flames are reaching the heavens.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I didn't know what it was, until later.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "That was still when I was quite new.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Actually, the whole time I was in Auschwitz I didn't know-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I didn't know so much.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "It was a short time that we were there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I don't know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Maybe some of the older people knew.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I know that somebody was saying that, like, we had a neighbor at home who [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] went there with her mother.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And-- and somebody came with a story that this girl went crazy.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "She was separated from her mother.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "She was, I remember, supposed to be an old maid.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "She might have been in her late 20s.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And-- and they brought back some horror stories now and then.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "How clear it was to most of my peers, I don't know-- what was happening.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
